data.description: Country living at its best! Beautiful 4.98 with lovely double wide modular home. Has a new 40x40 shop with a tiled office and A/C and 2 roll up doors. Storm Shelter off the large back deck that overlooks a huge backyard that includes an above ground pool. Storage shed and playhouse stay with property also. Tree stand in the woods stays. Nut and Fruit tree lure the deer in the fall. There are 3 bedroom but one could be divided to make a 4th. Huge family room that has a wood burning fireplace. Too many updates to name, this could be you daily retreat! Call your realtor to schedule a showing.
